        "stories": 2,
        "text": "Incredible opportunity to do a full renovation in one of the very best locations in the city! This generous sized lot and traditional colonial structure is waiting to be reimagined into your dream Duck Island home. Potential for incredible skyline views! Originally built as a duplex, this home is currently structured as a single family home with a generous back yard. This prime northern Duck Island location provides easy access to Tremont, Ohio City, the West Side Market, Downtown, the Towpath Trail, and more, making it an ideal place to live your best city life. Embrace the opportunity to create your perfect city home and experience the right blend of modern luxury and the best of city living."
